nodes.text: The Coruscant Holo Net: War on Wookiee World?

The Coruscant Holo Net: War on Wookiee World? was an in-universe issue of The Coruscant Holo Net that was published in Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.49. It was later reprinted in Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine 20. It extrapolated on events featured in the comic story Seeds.
